{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2024-01-03","name":"Herbert of Winchester Chamberlain of England","nameForms":[{"lang":"en","fullText":"Herbert of Winchester Chamberlain of England","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Herbert of Winchester"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Suffix","value":"Chamberlain of England"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"alternateName":"Herbert fitz Alberic","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1060–1119","fullLifespan":"Abt 1060–Abt 1119","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/goikm/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"DOCUMENT","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-904-96088-61-35/dist.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/99836369","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-904-96088-61-35/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-904-96088-61-35/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","headline":"Family of Herbert from Annals and Antiquities, vol. II, pg. 776-777","description":"Family of Herbert from Annuals and Antiquities, vol. II, pg. 776-777. However, it is noted, that Herbert of Vermandois (Herbertus Camerarius) was not the Count of Vermandois, but rather his uncle was, Herbert IV, Count of Vermandois. It is also noted that the son of Herbertus Camerarius, Henry FitzHerbert (Henry the Treasurer) is missing from the Annals and Antiquities, but his grandson Herbert (Herbert FitzHenry) and great grandson Herbert  (Herbert FitzHerbert) are included.","@type":"ImageObject"},{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7771-124099-3578-90/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/165477844","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/