":"英國越可爾約克","Winchester, Hampshire, England":"英國英格蘭哈普爾維古姆","Wales":"威爾士","lifeSummary":"Herbert of Winchester Chamberlain of England是Henry的兒子，於大約1060年出生在法國皮卡迪艾斯。他於1087年之前與Emma de Blois在威爾士結婚。他們至少是4個兒子和1個女兒的父母。他在英國英格蘭哈普爾維古姆被列為tenant-in-chief (under king henry ii)。他去世於大約1119年在英國英格蘭哈普爾維古姆享年61歲。"},"zh-hans":{"Abt 1060–Abt 1119":"大约1060年–大约1119年","1060–1119":"1060年–1119年","1075–1187":"1075年–1187年","1087–1155":"1087年–1155年","1088–Male":"1088年–殁","1089–Male":"1089年–殁","1091–Male":"1091年–殁","1094–Female":"1094年–殁","1040–Male":"1040年–殁","1091":"1091年","1066":"1066年","1088":"1088年","1187":"1187年","1087":"1087年","1075":"1075年","1040":"1040年","1094":"1094年","Abt 1119":"大约1119年","1060":"1060年","1089":"1089年","1155":"1155年","before 1087":"1087年之前","about 1087":"大约1087年","Abt 1060":"大约1060年","1119":"1119年","Vermandois, Aisne, Picardy, France":"法国皮卡迪艾斯","York, Yorkshire, England":"英国越可爾約克","Winchester, Hampshire, England":"英国英格兰哈普爾維古姆","Wales":"威尔士","lifeSummary":"Herbert of Winchester Chamberlain of England是Henry的儿子，于大约1060年出生在法国皮卡迪艾斯。他于1087年之前与Emma de Blois在威尔士结婚。他们至少是4个儿子和1个女儿的父母。他在英国英格兰哈普爾維古姆被列为tenant-in-chief (under king henry ii)。他去世于大约1119年在英国英格兰哈普爾維古姆享年61岁。"},"hr":{"Abt 1060–Abt 1119":"oko 1060.–oko 1119.","1060–1119":"1060–1119","1075–1187":"1075–1187","1087–1155":"1087–1155","1088–Male":"1088.–preminuo","1089–Male":"1089.–preminuo","1091–Male":"1091.–preminuo","1094–Female":"1094.–preminula","1040–Male":"1040–preminuo","1091":"1091.","1066":"1066.","1088":"1088.","1187":"1187","1087":"1087","1075":"1075","1040":"1040","1094":"1094.","Abt 1119":"oko 1119.","1060":"1060","1089":"1089.","1155":"1155","before 1087":"prije 1087.","about 1087":"oko 1087.","Abt 1060":"oko 1060.","1119":"1119","Vermandois, Aisne, Picardy, France":"Aisne, Picardie, Francuska","York, Yorkshire, England":"York, Yorkshire, England","Winchester, Hampshire, England":"Winchester, Hampshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Wales":"Wales"},"cs":{"Abt 1060–Abt 1119":"okolo 1060–okolo 1119","1060–1119":"1060–111